+# Overview Dashboard Implementation Plan
+
+> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.
+
+**Goal:** Replace root `/` of reports.yash.abysmallab.in with a global status dashboard grid.
+
+**Architecture:** Extend `generate-status-report.js` to produce a root `index.html` alongside per-project status pages. No runtime changes Î“Ă‡Ă¶ the app already serves static files from repo root via `express.static()`.
+
+**Tech Stack:** Node.js, vanilla JS/HTML/CSS (generator script), design tokens from ui-design skill.
+
+## Global Constraints
